<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #6b7280; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    .info-box { background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Subscription Canceled</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @owner.name %>,</p>

      <p>Your ChurchNeeds.net subscription has been canceled as requested.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Your subscription will remain active until:</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size: 20px; color: #0ea5e9; margin: 10px 0;"><%= @end_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280;">You'll continue to have full access until this date.</p>
      </div>

      <p>We're sorry to see you go! If there's anything we could have done better, we'd love to hear from you.</p>

      <p><strong>Changed your mind?</strong></p>
      <p>You can reactivate your subscription at any time before <%= @end_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= manage_donations_url %>" class="button">Reactivate Subscription</a>
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for supporting ChurchNeeds.net. We hope to serve you again in the future!</p>

      <p>Blessings,<br>The ChurchNeeds.net Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Roaring Lamb Productions<br>
      Questions? <a href="<%= new_contact_url %>">Contact our support team</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
